title: Mike Leigh/Jim Broadbent - A Sense of History - short - 1992
description:
<a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0105355/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0105355/</a>

This replaces a crappy version I upped a while back.

This classic portrayal of picaresque British country life will be hard for anyone to forget.

I saw it first paired, quite appropriately, with Peter Jackson's "Forgotten Silver".

Do yourself a favor...
